<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>BC Conseil Formation</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
   RESET & TOKENS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
:root{
  /* Site */
  --ink:#0e0e0e; --ink-60:rgba(14,14,14,.6); --ink-30:rgba(14,14,14,.3); --ink-10:rgba(14,14,14,.08);
  --sand:#f4f2ee; --sand-d:#eae7e1; --white:#fafafa;
  --accent-site:#1c5fff;
  /* RH Brand Palette */
  --rh-rose:#c0446a;     --rh-rose-light:#fdf0f4; --rh-rose-mid:rgba(192,68,106,.12);
  --rh-plum:#7c2d6b;     --rh-plum-light:#f8eef6;
  --rh-coral:#e05d3a;    --rh-coral-light:#fef2ee;
  --rh-warm:#d4856a;     --rh-gold:#b8893a;       --rh-gold-light:#fdf6e8;
  --rh-teal:#2a7a7a;     --rh-teal-light:#e6f4f4;
  /* Platform */
  --accent:#1c5fff; --accent-light:#eef2ff; --accent-mid:rgba(28,95,255,.15);
  --green:#0f9254; --green-bg:#e8f7ef;
  --amber:#b45309; --amber-bg:#fef3c7;
  --red:#dc2626; --red-bg:#fee2e2;
  --serif:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;
  --sans:'DM Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;
  --ease:cubic-bezier(.25,.1,.25,1);
  --ease-out:cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
  --r8:8px; --r12:12px; --r16:16px; --r24:24px;
  --shadow-s:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.06),0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
  --shadow-m:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08),0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
  --shadow-l:0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
}
html{font-size:15px;scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{font-family:var(--sans);background:var(--white);color:var(--ink);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-x:hidden;}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
   APP LAYERS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
#site-layer  { display:block; }
#login-layer { display:none; position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:2000; }
#app-layer   { display:none; position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:1000; }

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
   ██  S I T E  ██
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

/* Custom cursor */
.cursor{position:fixed;width:8px;height:8px;background:var(--ink);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;transition:transform .15s var(--ease),opacity .2s;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);}
.cursor-ring{position:fixed;width:36px;height:36px;border:1px solid rgba(14,14,14,.25);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;transition:width .3s var(--ease),height .3s var(--ease),opacity .3s;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav{
  position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:500;
  height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:0 48px;
  background:rgba(250,250,250,.88);
  backdrop-filter:blur(24px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(24px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);
  transition:border-color .4s;
}
.nav-logo{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.02em;color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none;}
.nav-logo em{font-style:italic;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink-60);}
.nav-links{display:flex;list-style:none;gap:32px;align-items:center;}
.nav-links a{font-size:12px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s;position:relative;}
.nav-links a::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-2px;left:0;width:0;height:1px;background:var(--ink);transition:width .3s var(--ease-out);}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--ink);}
.nav-links a:hover::after{width:100%;}
.nav-access{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  padding:10px 22px;
  background:var(--rh-rose);color:var(--white);
  font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;
  text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;border:none;
  transition:background .2s,transform .15s;
  font-family:var(--sans);
}
.nav-access:hover{background:var(--rh-plum);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.nav-access svg{flex-shrink:0;}

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero{height:100vh;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;padding-top:64px;position:relative;}
.hero-left{display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:80px 64px 80px 80px;border-right:1px solid var(--ink-10);position:relative;}
.hero-right{background:var(--sand);position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:64px;}

.hero-eyebrow{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);margin-bottom:36px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .9s var(--ease-out) .2s forwards;}
.hero-eyebrow::before{content:'';width:28px;height:1px;background:currentColor;flex-shrink:0;}
.hero-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(48px,5.5vw,84px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.025em;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:40px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .9s var(--ease-out) .4s forwards;}
.hero-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--ink-60);}
.hero-body{font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink-60);max-width:400px;margin-bottom:52px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .9s var(--ease-out) .6s forwards;}
.hero-actions{display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:center;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .9s var(--ease-out) .8s forwards;}

.btn-dark{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--white);background:var(--ink);padding:13px 26px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;transition:background .2s,transform .2s;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--sans);}
.btn-dark:hover{background:#2a2a2a;transform:translateY(-1px);}
.btn-ghost{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;transition:color .2s,gap .25s var(--ease-out);}
.btn-ghost:hover{color:var(--ink);gap:14px;}

/* Platform teaser pill in hero */
.platform-teaser{
  position:absolute;top:36px;right:40px;
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  background:white;border:1px solid var(--ink-10);
  border-radius:40px;padding:8px 16px 8px 8px;
  cursor:pointer;
  box-shadow:var(--shadow-s);
  transition:box-shadow .3s,transform .3s;
  opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .9s var(--ease-out) 1.1s forwards;
  z-index:2;
}
.platform-teaser:hover{box-shadow:var(--shadow-m);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.pt-dot{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--ink);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.pt-dot svg{color:white;}
.pt-text{font-size:12px;}
.pt-text strong{display:block;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);font-size:12px;}
.pt-text span{color:var(--ink-60);font-size:11px;}
.pt-arrow{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-60);margin-left:4px;}

.hero-right-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#fdf0f4 0%,#f8eef6 30%,#fdf6e8 60%,#e6f4f4 100%);}
.hero-right-lines{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(192,68,106,.07) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(192,68,106,.07) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;opacity:1;}
.hero-right-content{position:relative;z-index:2;}
.hero-quote{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(20px,2.8vw,34px);font-weight:300;font-style:italic;line-height:1.4;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.01em;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp 1.2s var(--ease-out) 1s forwards;}
.hero-quote-attr{margin-top:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);opacity:0;animation:fadeUp 1s var(--ease-out) 1.2s forwards;}

.scroll-hint{position:absolute;bottom:40px;left:80px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);opacity:0;animation:fadeUp 1s var(--ease-out) 1.3s forwards;}
.scroll-hint::before{content:'';width:36px;height:1px;background:currentColor;}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

/* ── SERVICES ── */
.services{padding:120px 80px;background:var(--white);}
.section-hd{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;margin-bottom:72px;align-items:end;}
.s-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.s-label::before{content:'';width:22px;height:1px;background:currentColor;}
.s-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(36px,4vw,58px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.025em;}
.s-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--ink-60);}
.s-desc{font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;color:var(--ink-60);}

.svc-list{border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);}
.svc-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:52px 1fr 1fr auto;gap:36px;align-items:start;padding:44px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:padding .4s var(--ease-out);}
.svc-item::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:var(--sand);transform:translateY(101%);transition:transform .5s var(--ease-out);z-index:0;}
.svc-item:hover::before{transform:translateY(0);}
.svc-item:hover{padding-left:16px;padding-right:16px;}
.svc-item>*{position:relative;z-index:1;}
.svc-num{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--ink-60);padding-top:5px;}
.svc-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(22px,2.2vw,34px);font-weight:400;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-.01em;}
.svc-name em{font-style:italic;}
.svc-desc{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;color:var(--ink-60);max-width:320px;padding-top:5px;}
.svc-tag{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);padding:7px 13px;border:1px solid var(--ink-10);white-space:nowrap;transition:border-color .3s,color .3s;}
.svc-item:hover .svc-tag{border-color:var(--ink-60);color:var(--ink);}

/* ── MANIFESTO ── */
.manifesto{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0e0e0e 0%,#1a0a14 50%,#0a0e1a 100%);padding:130px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.manifesto-grid{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:80px 80px;}
.manifesto-inner{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:920px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;}
.m-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-bottom:44px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:14px;}
.m-label::before,.m-label::after{content:'';width:28px;height:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);}
.m-text{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,56px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.25;color:rgba(255,255,255,.9);letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:72px;}
.m-text em{font-style:italic;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);}
.m-pillars{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);}
.pillar{background:var(--ink);padding:36px 28px;text-align:left;transition:background .3s;}
.pillar:hover{background:#161616;}
.pillar-n{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);margin-bottom:14px;}
.pillar-t{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.3;}
.pillar-p{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);}

/* ── PCRH ── */
.pcrh{background:var(--sand);padding:120px 80px;}
.pcrh-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:120px;align-items:center;}
.pcrh-visual{position:relative;aspect-ratio:3/4;max-height:520px;}
.pcrh-frame{position:absolute;inset:0;background:white;border:1px solid var(--sand-d);display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:36px;overflow:hidden;}
.pcrh-frame-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg,transparent,transparent 28px,rgba(14,14,14,.025) 28px,rgba(14,14,14,.025) 29px);}
.pcrh-frame-word{position:relative;z-index:1;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:48px;font-weight:300;line-height:1;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.03em;}
.pcrh-frame-word span{display:block;font-style:italic;color:var(--ink-60);font-size:34px;}
.pcrh-accent{position:absolute;top:-18px;right:-18px;width:72px;height:72px;background:var(--ink);}
.pcrh-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:white;background:var(--ink);padding:6px 14px;margin-bottom:36px;}
.pcrh-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(32px,3.5vw,48px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:24px;}
.pcrh-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--ink-60);}
.pcrh-p{font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink-60);margin-bottom:40px;}
.pcrh-list{list-style:none;margin-bottom:44px;}
.pcrh-list li{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink);padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--sand-d);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;transition:padding-left .25s var(--ease-out);}
.pcrh-list li::before{content:'—';color:var(--ink-60);font-size:11px;flex-shrink:0;}
.pcrh-list li:hover{padding-left:8px;}

/* ── CTA STRIP ── */
.cta-strip{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:40px;padding:0 80px;min-height:110px;background:var(--white);border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);}
.cta-text{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(22px,2.8vw,38px);font-weight:300;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.2;}
.cta-text em{font-style:italic;color:var(--ink-60);}

/* ── PLATFORM CTA CARD ── */
.platform-cta-section{padding:80px;background:var(--sand);border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);}
.platform-cta-card{
  background:var(--ink);border-radius:20px;
  padding:56px 64px;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:60px;align-items:center;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.platform-cta-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;right:-60px;top:-60px;width:320px;height:320px;border-radius:50%;border:80px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03);}
.platform-cta-card::after{content:'';position:absolute;right:80px;bottom:-80px;width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;border:50px solid rgba(255,255,255,.025);}
.pcc-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-bottom:16px;}
.pcc-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,48px);font-weight:300;color:white;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:14px;}
.pcc-title em{font-style:italic;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);}
.pcc-sub{font-size:14px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);line-height:1.65;max-width:480px;}
.pcc-right{position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:16px;flex-shrink:0;}
.btn-platform{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  padding:14px 28px;
  background:white;color:var(--ink);
  font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.03em;
  cursor:pointer;border:none;font-family:var(--sans);
  border-radius:4px;
  transition:background .2s,transform .2s,box-shadow .2s;
  white-space:nowrap;
}
.btn-platform:hover{background:#f0f0f0;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.3);}
.pcc-note{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);text-align:center;letter-spacing:.03em;}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer{background:var(--sand);border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);padding:72px 80px 40px;}
.footer-top{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:72px;padding-bottom:56px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);margin-bottom:36px;}
.footer-brand{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:20px;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:14px;letter-spacing:-.01em;}
.footer-tagline{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink-60);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:18px;}
.footer-col-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);margin-bottom:18px;}
.footer-links{list-style:none;}
.footer-links li{margin-bottom:11px;}
.footer-links a{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink-60);text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s;}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--ink);}
.footer-bottom{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.footer-copy{font-size:12px;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink-60);}
.footer-legal{display:flex;gap:28px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.footer-legal span{font-size:12px;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink-60);}

/* Scroll reveal */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px);transition:opacity .8s var(--ease-out),transform .8s var(--ease-out);}
.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:none;}
.d1{transition-delay:.1s;} .d2{transition-delay:.2s;} .d3{transition-delay:.3s;}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
   LOGIN MODAL
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.login-overlay{
  position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:rgba(14,14,14,.55);
  backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
.login-box{
  background:var(--white);width:100%;max-width:420px;
  border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;
  box-shadow:var(--shadow-l);
  animation:loginIn .4s var(--ease-out);
}
@keyframes loginIn{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(.95) translateY(16px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.login-header{background:var(--ink);padding:36px 40px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.login-header::before{content:'';position:absolute;right:-40px;top:-40px;width:180px;height:180px;border-radius:50%;border:50px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);}
.login-brand{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:20px;font-weight:300;color:white;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.login-brand em{font-style:italic;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);}
.login-sub{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);margin-top:6px;position:relative;z-index:1;font-weight:300;}
.login-body{padding:36px 40px;}
.login-label{display:block;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);margin-bottom:7px;}
.login-input{
  width:100%;padding:12px 16px;
  border:1px solid var(--ink-10);background:var(--sand);
  border-radius:var(--r8);font-size:14px;font-family:var(--sans);
  color:var(--ink);outline:none;margin-bottom:18px;
  transition:border-color .2s,box-shadow .2s;
}
.login-input:focus{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-mid);}
.login-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:20px;}
.login-remember{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-60);cursor:pointer;}
.login-remember input{cursor:pointer;}
.login-forgot{font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;}
.login-submit{
  width:100%;padding:13px;
  background:var(--ink);color:white;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:500;font-family:var(--sans);
  border:none;border-radius:var(--r8);
  cursor:pointer;transition:background .2s,transform .15s;
  letter-spacing:.03em;
}
.login-submit:hover{background:#2a2a2a;transform:translateY(-1px);}
.login-divider{text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-30);margin:16px 0;position:relative;}
.login-divider::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:50%;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:var(--ink-10);}
.login-divider span{background:var(--white);padding:0 10px;position:relative;}
.login-register{
  width:100%;padding:12px;
  background:transparent;color:var(--ink);
  font-size:13px;font-weight:400;font-family:var(--sans);
  border:1px solid var(--ink-10);border-radius:var(--r8);
  cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .2s,background .2s;
}
.login-register:hover{border-color:var(--ink-30);background:var(--sand);}
.login-close{
  position:absolute;top:16px;right:16px;
  width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;
  border:none;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:white;
  font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  transition:background .2s;z-index:2;
}
.login-close:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);}
.login-footer{padding:16px 40px;background:var(--sand);border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);text-align:center;}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
   ██  P L A T F O R M  ██
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
/* App shell */
.app-shell{
  display:flex;
  min-height:100vh;
  background:var(--sand);
  overflow:hidden;
}

/* Sidebar */
.sidebar{
  width:236px;
  min-width:236px;
  height:100vh;
  position:sticky;
  top:0;
  flex-shrink:0;
  background:var(--ink);
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  overflow-y:auto;
}
@media (max-width: 1024px){

  .sidebar{
    position:fixed;
    left:-236px;
    z-index:1000;
    transition:.3s;
  }

  .sidebar.open{
    left:0;
  }

}
/* Scrollbar propre */
.sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar{
  width:6px;
}
.sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  border-radius:20px;
}

/* Logo */
.sb-logo{
  padding:22px 18px 18px;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
}

.sb-logo-top{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
}

.sb-brand{
  font-family:var(--serif);
  font-size:17px;
  font-weight:400;
  color:#fff;
  letter-spacing:-.01em;
}

.sb-brand em{
  font-style:italic;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);
}

.sb-tag{
  font-size:9px;
  font-weight:600;
  letter-spacing:.08em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  background:rgba(28,95,255,.3);
  color:#6fa3ff;
  padding:3px 8px;
  border-radius:4px;
}

.sb-sub{
  font-size:10px;
  letter-spacing:.07em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);
  margin-top:4px;
}

/* Sections */
.sb-section{
  padding:18px 12px 6px;
  font-size:10px;
  letter-spacing:.09em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.22);
}

/* Navigation */
.nav-item{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:10px;
  padding:9px 10px;
  margin:1px 8px;
  border-radius:var(--r8);
  font-size:13px;
  font-weight:400;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .15s ease;
  user-select:none;
}

.nav-item:hover{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.82);
  transform:translateX(2px);
}

.nav-item.active{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),#6366f1);
  color:#fff;
  font-weight:500;
  box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
}

.nav-item .ni{
  width:15px;
  height:15px;
  flex-shrink:0;
  opacity:.65;
}

.nav-item.active .ni{
  opacity:1;
}

.nb{
  margin-left:auto;
  font-size:10px;
  font-weight:600;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);
  padding:2px 7px;
  border-radius:20px;
}

.nav-item.active .nb{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);
  color:#fff;
}

/* Footer utilisateur */
.sb-exit{
  margin-top:auto;
  padding:14px 12px;
  border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:10px;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:background .15s;
}

.sb-exit:hover{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
}

.sb-avatar{
  width:30px;
  height:30px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1c5fff,#8b5cf6);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  font-size:11px;
  font-weight:600;
  color:#fff;
  flex-shrink:0;
}

.sb-user-name{
  font-size:12px;
  font-weight:500;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);
}

.sb-user-role{
  font-size:10px;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);
}

.sb-exit-icon{
  margin-left:auto;
  opacity:.3;
  font-size:13px;
}

/* Main */
.app-main{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;overflow-x:hidden;}
.topbar{height:58px;background:var(--white);border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 26px;gap:14px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;}
.topbar-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:20px;font-weight:400;flex:1;color:var(--ink);}
.topbar-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--ink-60);}
.tb-search{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:var(--sand);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);border-radius:var(--r8);padding:7px 13px;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-60);width:200px;}
.icon-btn{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:var(--r8);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--ink-60);transition:background .15s;position:relative;}
.icon-btn:hover{background:var(--sand);}
.notif-dot{position:absolute;top:5px;right:5px;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);border:1.5px solid var(--white);}
.view{display:none;padding:26px;animation:fadeIn .25s var(--ease);}
.view.active{display:block;}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(5px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

/* Platform generic */
.card{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r16);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);overflow:hidden;}
.cp{padding:20px 22px;}
.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
.g4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;}
.row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.rb{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;}
.col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;}
.lbl{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);}
.ts{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.01em;}
.bxs{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-60);}
.bxxs{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);}
.tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;}
.tb{background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--accent);}
.tg{background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green);}
.ta{background:var(--amber-bg);color:var(--amber);}
.tgr{background:var(--sand);color:var(--ink-60);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:var(--r8);font-size:12px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;font-family:var(--sans);}
.bp{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;} .bp:hover{background:#2a2a2a;transform:translateY(-1px);}
.bo{background:transparent;color:var(--ink);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);} .bo:hover{border-color:var(--ink-30);background:var(--sand);}
.ba{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;} .ba:hover{background:#1249e0;}
.bs{padding:6px 12px;font-size:11px;}
.pb{height:5px;background:var(--ink-10);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;}
.pf{height:100%;border-radius:3px;background:var(--accent);}
.pf.g{background:var(--green);}

/* Dashboard */
.dash-hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ink) 0%,#1a0a14 60%,#0e0e1a 100%);border-radius:var(--r16);padding:32px 38px;margin-bottom:18px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:40px;align-items:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.dash-hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;right:-40px;top:-40px;width:260px;height:260px;border-radius:50%;border:60px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);}
.dh-greet{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-bottom:8px;}
.dh-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:28px;font-weight:300;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:6px;}
.dh-name em{font-style:italic;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);}
.dh-sub{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.38);max-width:380px;line-height:1.6;}
.dh-btn{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);font-size:12px;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.dh-btn:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.18);transform:none;}
.stat-m{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r12);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);padding:16px 18px;}
.sm-val{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:28px;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:2px;}
.sm-lbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);}
.sm-d{font-size:11px;color:var(--green);margin-top:3px;}
.fr{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);cursor:pointer;transition:padding-left .2s;}
.fr:last-child{border-bottom:none;} .fr:hover{padding-left:4px;}
.fth{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:var(--r8);flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:16px;font-weight:300;color:#fff;}
.fth.c1{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1c5fff,#6366f1);}
.fth.c2{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f9254,#34d399);}
.fth.c3{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b45309,#f59e0b);}
.fth.c4{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#a78bfa);}
.fm{flex:1;min-width:0;}
.fn{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.fs{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);margin-top:2px;}
.ai{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:11px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);}
.ai:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.ad{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;}
.ad.g{background:var(--green);} .ad.a{background:#f59e0b;}
.at{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink);}
.at strong{font-weight:500;}
.atime{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink-30);margin-top:1px;}

/* Catalogue */
.cc{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r16);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .25s var(--ease-out),box-shadow .25s,border-color .2s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.cc:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:var(--shadow-l);border-color:rgba(28,95,255,.2);}
.cb{height:108px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:22px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(255,255,255,.9);}
.cbody{padding:16px 18px;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.ct{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.3;}
.cd{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-60);line-height:1.55;flex:1;margin-bottom:12px;}
.cfooter{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:auto;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);}
.cp2{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;}

/* Apprenant */
.mi{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r12);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);margin-bottom:7px;overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow .2s;}
.mi:hover{box-shadow:var(--shadow-m);}
.mh{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:14px 18px;cursor:pointer;}
.ms{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--ink-10);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;flex-shrink:0;}
.ms.done{background:var(--green-bg);border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green);}
.ms.curr{background:var(--accent-light);border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}
.ms.lock{background:var(--sand);color:var(--ink-30);}
.minfo{flex:1;}
.mtitle{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;}
.msub{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);margin-top:1px;}
.mdur{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);}
.mexp{padding:0 18px 14px 56px;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-60);line-height:1.6;border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);display:none;}
.mi.open .mexp{display:block;}

/* Messagerie */
.mwrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:260px 1fr;height:calc(100vh - 110px);background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r16);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);overflow:hidden;}
.mlist{border-right:1px solid var(--ink-10);overflow-y:auto;}
.mlh{padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;}
.msrch{padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);}
.msrch input{width:100%;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:var(--r8);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);background:var(--sand);font-size:12px;font-family:var(--sans);outline:none;color:var(--ink);}
.mitem{padding:12px 16px;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;transition:background .15s;}
.mitem:hover{background:var(--sand);}
.mitem.active{background:var(--accent-light);}
.min-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;}
.min-prev{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;margin-top:1px;}
.mtime{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink-30);flex-shrink:0;}
.munread{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);margin-top:3px;flex-shrink:0;}
.mmain{display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;}
.mhdr{padding:14px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.mhdr-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;}
.mhdr-status{font-size:11px;color:var(--green);}
.mbody{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:18px 20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;background:var(--sand);}
.bubble{max-width:68%;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:var(--r12);font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;}
.bubble.them{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);color:var(--ink);border-bottom-left-radius:3px;align-self:flex-start;}
.bubble.me{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border-bottom-right-radius:3px;align-self:flex-end;}
.btime{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink-30);margin-top:3px;}
.btime.r{text-align:right;}
.minput-bar{padding:12px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;}
.minput{flex:1;padding:9px 14px;border-radius:var(--r8);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);background:var(--sand);font-size:12px;font-family:var(--sans);outline:none;color:var(--ink);}
.minput:focus{border-color:var(--accent);}

/* Admin */
.mc{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r16);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);padding:20px 22px;}
.mv{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:32px;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.03em;}
.mlbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);margin-top:3px;}
.mtr{font-size:11px;margin-top:6px;}
.mtr.up{color:var(--green);} .mtr.dn{color:var(--red);}
.tw{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r16);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);overflow:hidden;}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;}
thead{background:var(--sand);}
th{padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);}
td{padding:10px 14px;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink);border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);}
tr:hover td{background:var(--sand);}
.ava{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}

/* Profil */
.ph{background:var(--ink);border-radius:var(--r16);padding:36px;margin-bottom:18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:28px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.ph::before{content:'';position:absolute;right:-50px;top:-50px;width:240px;height:240px;border-radius:50%;border:60px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03);}
.pav{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1c5fff,#8b5cf6);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:24px;font-weight:300;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;z-index:1;border:3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);}
.pinfo{position:relative;z-index:1;}
.pname{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:24px;font-weight:300;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.01em;}
.prole{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);margin-top:3px;}
.pbadges{display:flex;gap:7px;margin-top:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.pbadge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:4px 11px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);}
.skbar{margin-bottom:12px;}
.sklbl{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:4px;}
.skpct{color:var(--ink-60);}

/* ─ scrollbar ─ */
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px;height:4px;}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent;}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--ink-10);border-radius:2px;}

/* ─ Responsive ─ */
@media(max-width:960px){
  nav{padding:0 20px;}
  nav ul{display:none;}
  .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .hero-right{display:none;}
  .hero-left{padding:60px 20px;}
  .scroll-hint{display:none;}
  .services,.manifesto,.pcrh,.cta-strip,.platform-cta-section{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;}
  .section-hd,.pcrh-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:32px;}
  .svc-item{grid-template-columns:40px 1fr;grid-template-rows:auto auto;}
  .svc-desc{grid-column:2;}.svc-tag{display:none;}
  .m-pillars{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .pcrh-visual{display:none;}
  .footer-top{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px;}
  footer{padding:48px 20px 32px;}
  .platform-cta-card{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:28px;}
}

  /* ═══ TRUST BAND ═══ */
  .trust-band{
    background:var(--white);
    border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink-10);
    padding:52px 80px;
  }
  .trust-inner{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:28px;}
  .trust-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-60);}
  .trust-logos{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:48px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;}
  .trust-logo-item{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
  .trust-img{display:block;object-fit:contain;}
  .qualiopi-img{height:80px;width:auto;filter:none;}
  .qualianor-img{height:72px;width:auto;border-radius:8px;}
  .trust-divider{width:1px;height:64px;background:var(--ink-10);flex-shrink:0;}
  .trust-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-60);text-align:center;max-width:400px;line-height:1.5;}
  .trust-note strong{color:var(--ink);font-weight:500;}

  /* ═══ AI SECTION ═══ */
  .ai-section{
    background:#080808;
    padding:130px 80px;
    position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  }
  .ai-grid-bg{
    position:absolute;inset:0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(28,95,255,.06) 1px,transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(28,95,255,.06) 1px,transparent 1px);
    background-size:64px 64px;
  }
  .ai-inner{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;}
  .ai-header{margin-bottom:64px;}

  .ai-cards{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
    gap:16px;
  }

  .ai-card{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:28px 28px 24px;
    position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    transition:background .3s,border-color .3s,transform .3s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .ai-card:hover{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
    border-color:rgba(28,95,255,.3);
    transform:translateY(-3px);
  }
  .ai-card--featured{
    grid-column:span 1;
    background:rgba(28,95,255,.08);
    border-color:rgba(28,95,255,.2);
  }
  .ai-card-glow{
    position:absolute;inset:0;
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%,rgba(28,95,255,.12),transparent 60%);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .ai-card-tag{
    font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:rgba(28,95,255,.8);margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  .ai-card-title{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-size:24px;font-weight:300;
    color:#fff;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  .ai-card-desc{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:20px;}

  /* Terminal demo */
  .ai-demo{margin-bottom:20px;}
  .ai-demo-label{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);margin-bottom:8px;}
  .ai-terminal{
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.5);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;
    font-size:12px;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;
  }
  .ai-terminal-line{color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;}
  .ai-prompt{flex-shrink:0;font-size:11px;}
  .ai-green{color:#34d399;}
  .ai-amber{color:#f59e0b;}
  .ai-typing{animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;}
  @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.6}}

  /* Path visual */
  .ai-visual{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .ai-path-node{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);padding:6px 12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:20px;white-space:nowrap;}
  .ai-path-node.active{color:#fff;border-color:rgba(28,95,255,.5);background:rgba(28,95,255,.15);}
  .ai-path-arrow{color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;}

  /* Chat demo */
  .ai-chat-demo{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;margin-bottom:20px;}
  .ai-chat-bubble{font-size:12px;padding:9px 13px;border-radius:10px;line-height:1.5;}
  .ai-chat-bubble.user{background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);align-self:flex-end;border-bottom-right-radius:3px;}
  .ai-chat-bubble.bot{background:rgba(28,95,255,.15);color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);border-bottom-left-radius:3px;border:1px solid rgba(28,95,255,.2);}

  /* Counter */
  .ai-counter{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-bottom:20px;padding:16px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);border-radius:8px;}
  .ai-counter-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;}
  .ai-counter-val{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:26px;font-weight:300;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.02em;}
  .ai-counter-lbl{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);letter-spacing:.04em;}
  .ai-counter-sep{width:1px;height:40px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);}

  /* Tech stack */
  .ai-stack{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .ai-tech{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.04em;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);padding:3px 10px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:20px;}

  /* Integrations */
  .ai-integrations{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}
  .ai-int-row{display:flex;gap:10px;}
  .ai-int-chip{
    flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;
    font-size:12px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);
    transition:background .2s,border-color .2s;cursor:default;
  }
  .ai-int-chip:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.09);border-color:rgba(28,95,255,.3);}
  .ai-sovereignty{
    font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-top:4px;
  }
  .ai-sov-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:#34d399;flex-shrink:0;}

  @media(max-width:960px){
    .trust-band{padding:40px 20px;}
    .trust-logos{gap:24px;}
    .ai-section{padding:80px 20px;}
    .ai-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .ai-card{grid-column:span 1 !important;}
    .ai-integrations .ai-int-row{flex-direction:column;}
  }


  /* ─── RH COLOR SERVICES ─── */
  .svc-item.svc-rose::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--rh-rose-light),#fff8fa);}
  .svc-item.svc-plum::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--rh-plum-light),#faf6f9);}
  .svc-item.svc-teal::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--rh-teal-light),#f0f8f8);}
  .svc-item.svc-rose:hover .svc-tag{border-color:var(--rh-rose);color:var(--rh-rose);}
  .svc-item.svc-plum:hover .svc-tag{border-color:var(--rh-plum);color:var(--rh-plum);}
  .svc-item.svc-teal:hover .svc-tag{border-color:var(--rh-teal);color:var(--rh-teal);}
  .svc-num-rose{color:var(--rh-rose)!important;}
  .svc-num-plum{color:var(--rh-plum)!important;}
  .svc-num-teal{color:var(--rh-teal)!important;}
  .svc-item.svc-rose:hover .svc-num-rose,.svc-item.svc-plum:hover .svc-num-plum,.svc-item.svc-teal:hover .svc-num-teal{font-weight:600;}

  /* ─── HERO FLOATING ORBS ─── */
  .hero-orb{position:absolute;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(60px);pointer-events:none;animation:orbFloat 8s ease-in-out infinite;}
  .hero-orb-1{width:300px;height:300px;background:rgba(192,68,106,.18);top:-60px;right:20%;animation-delay:0s;}
  .hero-orb-2{width:200px;height:200px;background:rgba(124,45,107,.14);bottom:20%;right:5%;animation-delay:-3s;}
  .hero-orb-3{width:180px;height:180px;background:rgba(184,137,58,.12);top:40%;right:40%;animation-delay:-5s;}
  @keyframes orbFloat{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0) scale(1)}50%{transform:translateY(-20px) scale(1.05)}}

  /* ─── HERO QUOTE COLORED ─── */
  .hero-quote{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(20px,2.8vw,34px);font-weight:300;font-style:italic;line-height:1.4;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.01em;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp 1.2s var(--ease-out) 1s forwards;}
  .hero-quote strong{color:var(--rh-rose);font-weight:400;font-style:normal;}

  /* ─── SECTION LABEL ACCENTED ─── */
  .s-label.rose{color:var(--rh-rose);}
  .s-label.plum{color:var(--rh-plum);}
  .s-label.teal{color:var(--rh-teal);}

  /* ─── PCRH ACCENT COLORED ─── */
  .pcrh-accent{position:absolute;top:-18px;right:-18px;width:72px;height:72px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--rh-rose),var(--rh-plum));}
  .pcrh-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:white;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--rh-rose),var(--rh-plum));padding:6px 14px;margin-bottom:36px;}

  /* ─── BTN DARK HOVER ─── */
  .btn-dark:hover{background:var(--rh-rose);transform:translateY(-1px);}

  /* ─── PLATFORM TEASER PILL COLORED ─── */
  .pt-dot{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--rh-rose),var(--rh-plum));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
  
  /* ─── HERO LEFT accent line ─── */
  .hero-eyebrow::before{content:'';width:28px;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--rh-rose),var(--rh-plum));flex-shrink:0;}

  /* ─── MANIFESTO PILLARS NUMBERED ─── */
  .pillar:nth-child(1) .pillar-n{color:rgba(192,68,106,.6);}
  .pillar:nth-child(2) .pillar-n{color:rgba(124,45,107,.6);}
  .pillar:nth-child(3) .pillar-n{color:rgba(42,122,122,.6);}

  /* ─── TRUST BAND WARM ─── */
  .trust-band{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--rh-rose-light) 0%,var(--rh-plum-light) 50%,var(--rh-teal-light) 100%);border-top:1px solid rgba(192,68,106,.12);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(192,68,106,.12);padding:52px 80px;}

  /* ─── CTA STRIP COLORED ─── */
  .cta-strip{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:40px;padding:0 80px;min-height:110px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--rh-rose-light),var(--rh-plum-light));border-top:1px solid rgba(192,68,106,.12);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(192,68,106,.12);}

  /* ─── PLATFORM CTA CARD COLORED ─── */
  .platform-cta-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--rh-plum) 0%,#1a0a14 40%,#0a0e1a 100%);}
  .pcc-label{color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);}

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer{background:var(--ink);}
  .footer-brand,.footer-col-label,.footer-bottom{color:#fff;}
  .footer-tagline{color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);}
  .footer-links a{color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);}
  .footer-links a:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);}
  .footer-bottom{border-top-color:rgba(255,255,255,.07);}
  .footer-copy,.footer-legal span{color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);}
  .footer-col-label{color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);}

  /* ─── NAV IA link accent ─── */
  .nav-links li:last-of-type a{color:var(--rh-rose);}
  .nav-links li:last-of-type a:hover{color:var(--rh-plum);}
  .nav-links li:last-of-type a::after{background:var(--rh-rose);}


  /* ─── PLATFORM AI FEATURES ─── */
  .ai-plat-card{
    background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);border-radius:var(--r12);
    padding:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;
    cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .ai-plat-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:var(--shadow-m);transform:translateY(-1px);}
  .ai-plat-icon{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--r8);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
  .ai-plat-content{flex:1;min-width:0;}
  .ai-plat-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:2px;}
  .ai-plat-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-60);line-height:1.45;}
  .ai-plat-arrow{color:var(--ink-30);font-size:14px;transition:transform .2s;flex-shrink:0;}
  .ai-plat-card:hover .ai-plat-arrow{transform:translateX(4px);color:var(--accent);}

  @keyframes slideIn{from{transform:translateX(100%);opacity:0}to{transform:none;opacity:1}}

  .ai-panel-content{display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100%;}
  .ai-panel-header{padding:28px 24px;position:relative;flex-shrink:0;}
  .ai-panel-chat{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;background:var(--sand);}
  .ai-panel-input{padding:12px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--ink-10);display:flex;gap:8px;background:var(--white);}
  .ai-input-field{flex:1;padding:9px 14px;border-radius:var(--r8);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);background:var(--sand);font-size:12px;font-family:var(--sans);outline:none;color:var(--ink);}
  .ai-input-field:focus{border-color:var(--accent);}
  .ai-msg{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;}
  .ai-msg.user{flex-direction:row-reverse;}
  .ai-msg-avatar{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
  .ai-msg-bubble{max-width:85%;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:var(--r12);font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;}
  .ai-msg-bubble.bot{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--ink-10);color:var(--ink);border-bottom-left-radius:3px;}
  .ai-msg-bubble.user{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border-bottom-right-radius:3px;}
  .ai-typing-dots{display:inline-flex;gap:4px;align-items:center;height:16px;}
  .ai-typing-dots span{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--ink-30);animation:dotPulse 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;}
  .ai-typing-dots span:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.2s;}
  .ai-typing-dots span:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.4s;}
  @keyframes dotPulse{0%,80%,100%{transform:scale(.7);opacity:.4}40%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}}
  .quiz-opt{width:100%;padding:12px 16px;border:1px solid var(--ink-10);border-radius:var(--r8);background:var(--white);text-align:left;font-size:13px;font-family:var(--sans);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;color:var(--ink);}
  .quiz-opt:hover{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-light);}
  .quiz-opt.correct{background:var(--green-bg);border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green);}
  .quiz-opt.wrong{background:var(--red-bg,#fee2e2);border-color:var(--red,#dc2626);color:var(--red,#dc2626);}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════╗ -->
<!-- ║              CUSTOM CURSOR               ║ -->
<!-- ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════╝ -->
<div class="cursor" id="cur"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="ring"></div>

<!-- ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════╗ -->
<!-- ║             SITE VITRINE                 ║ -->
<!-- ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════╝ -->
<div id="site-layer">

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="BC Conseil Formation" style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;"></a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#formation">Formation</a></li>
      <li><a href="#conseil">Conseil</a></li>
      <li><a href="#pcrh">PCRH</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ia">IA & Innovation</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="nav-access" onclick="openLogin()">
      <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="2" y="1" width="12" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M5 8h6M8 5v6"/></svg>
      Accéder à la plateforme
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="accueil">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Ressources Humaines · Droit · Stratégie</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">La performance<br>humaine comme<br><em>avantage décisif.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-body">Nous accompagnons les organisations dans le développement de leurs pratiques RH — de la formation au conseil stratégique, jusqu'à l'audit.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#formation" class="btn-dark">Nos expertises</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-ghost">Prendre contact →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-hint">Défiler</div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-right">
      <div class="hero-right-bg"></div>
      <div class="hero-right-lines"></div>

      <!-- Platform teaser pill -->
      <div class="platform-teaser" onclick="openLogin()">
        <div class="pt-dot">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M8 1L14 4.5V11L8 14.5L2 11V4.5L8 1z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-text">
          <strong>Espace apprenant</strong>
          <span>Accéder à mes formations</span>
        </div>
        <span class="pt-arrow">→</span>
      </div>

      <div style="position:absolute;top:32px;left:40px;z-index:3;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .9s var(--ease-out) .9s forwards;">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="BC Conseil Formation logo" style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;filter:drop-shadow(0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.15));">
      </div>
      <div class="hero-right-content">
      <blockquote class="hero-quote">"Valorisez vos talents,<br>façonnez votre avenir."</blockquote>
        <p class="hero-quote-attr">— BC Conseil Formation</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="services" id="formation">
    <div class="section-hd">
      <div>
        <p class="s-label reveal">01 — Expertises</p>
        <h2 class="s-title reveal">Nos domaines<br><em>d'intervention.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p class="s-desc reveal">Trois axes complémentaires pour transformer durablement la performance de vos équipes et la structuration de votre organisation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-list">
      <div class="svc-item reveal svc-rose" id="conseil">
        <span class="svc-num svc-num-rose">01</span>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Formation en <em>Ressources Humaines</em> & Droit</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Recrutement, gestion des talents, développement des compétences, droit du travail — des programmes adaptés à votre secteur et vos enjeux.</p>
        <span class="svc-tag">Formation</span>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-item reveal svc-plum">
        <span class="svc-num svc-num-plum">02</span>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Conseil en RH, <em>Organisation</em> & Stratégie</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Identification de vos défis, développement de stratégies personnalisées — un accompagnement expert qui aligne vos ressources avec vos objectifs.</p>
        <span class="svc-tag">Conseil</span>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-item reveal svc-teal">
        <span class="svc-num svc-num-teal">03</span>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Audit RH & <em>Organisation</em> du travail</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Diagnostic rigoureux de vos pratiques, conformité réglementaire, identification des leviers d'amélioration — pour une organisation durable.</p>
        <span class="svc-tag">Audit</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MANIFESTO -->
  <section class="manifesto">
    <div class="manifesto-grid"></div>
    <div class="manifesto-inner">
      <p class="m-label reveal">Notre philosophie</p>
      <p class="m-text reveal">Chaque organisation est un système humain unique. Nous n'appliquons pas de <em>formules génériques</em> — nous construisons des réponses précises, ancrées dans votre réalité.</p>
      <div class="m-pillars">
        <div class="pillar reveal"><p class="pillar-n">I</p><h3 class="pillar-t">Expertise sectorielle</h3><p class="pillar-p">Une connaissance approfondie des dynamiques propres à votre secteur, pour des interventions immédiatement opérationnelles.</p></div>
        <div class="pillar reveal d1"><p class="pillar-n">II</p><h3 class="pillar-t">Approche sur mesure</h3><p class="pillar-p">Aucune solution standardisée. Chaque mission est conçue spécifiquement selon vos enjeux, votre culture et vos objectifs.</p></div>
        <div class="pillar reveal d2"><p class="pillar-n">III</p><h3 class="pillar-t">Certification Qualiopi</h3><p class="pillar-p">Une garantie de qualité certifiée, permettant le financement de vos formations par les OPCO et les dispositifs publics.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PCRH -->
  <section class="pcrh" id="pcrh">
    <div class="pcrh-inner">
      <div class="pcrh-visual reveal">
        <div class="pcrh-frame">
          <div class="pcrh-frame-bg"></div>
          <div class="pcrh-frame-word">PCRH<span>Conseil RH</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pcrh-accent"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="pcrh-tag reveal">Dispositif d'État</span>
        <h2 class="pcrh-title reveal">Un accompagnement<br><em>financé</em> pour structurer<br>votre fonction RH.</h2>
        <p class="pcrh-p reveal">La Prestation de Conseil en Ressources Humaines (PCRH) est un dispositif cofinancé par l'État, destiné aux TPE et PME pour professionnaliser la gestion RH.</p>
        <ul class="pcrh-list reveal">
          <li>Diagnostic complet de votre organisation RH</li>
          <li>Définition d'un plan d'action structuré</li>
          <li>Accompagnement à la mise en œuvre</li>
          <li>Financement partiel ou total par l'État</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-dark reveal">Vérifier mon éligibilité</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- TRUST BADGES: Qualiopi + Qualianor -->
  <div class="trust-band">
    <div class="trust-inner">
      <div class="trust-label">Organismes certificateurs</div>
      <div class="trust-logos">
        <div class="trust-logo-item">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Qualiopi — Processus certifié" class="trust-img qualiopi-img">
        </div>
        <div class="trust-divider"></div>
        <div class="trust-logo-item">
          <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Qualianor — Organisme certifié Qualiopi RNQ" class="trust-img qualianor-img">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-note">Certification qualité délivrée au titre de la catégorie <strong>Action de formation</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- AI / LLM SECTION -->
  <section class="ai-section" id="ia">
    <div class="ai-grid-bg"></div>
    <div class="ai-inner">

      <div class="ai-header">
        <p class="s-label reveal" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);">05 — Intelligence Artificielle</p>
        <h2 class="s-title reveal" style="color:#fff;">La RH augmentée<br>par <em style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.45)">l'IA.</em></h2>
        <p class="s-desc reveal" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);max-width:560px;margin-top:16px;">Nous intégrons des solutions LLM de pointe dans nos accompagnements pour accélérer votre transformation RH — analyse, génération, aide à la décision.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-cards">

        <div class="ai-card ai-card--featured reveal">
